urls.title: Ivermectin for Prevention and Treatment of COVID-19... : American Journal of Therapeutics
urls.description: mortality, in secondary outcomes, and in chemoprophylaxis, among people with, or at high risk of, COVID-19 infection. Data sources: We searched bibliographic databases up to April 25, 2021. Two review authors sifted for studies, extracted data, and assessed risk of bias.
